\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p'=[0,\cos\theta\mathbf{p}+\sin\theta\hat{\mathbf{v}}\times\mathbf{p}]
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
现在，让我们找一个例子来测试上面的公式。譬如向量
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{p}$
\end_inset

绕
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

轴(就是
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

